<plot>The underworld of Cairo is alerted to certain moves of various people in the search for Rommel's treasure. Some are intent on the valuables, while others seek only the documents. The searchers, each working for individual raesons, are: von Brunner (Paul Christian), an ex-officer of Rommel's staff who seeks the treasure to aid families of the fallen; Wells (Bruce Cabot), a famous American news photographer out for a scoop; Mrs. Fischer (Isa Miranda), owner of a luxury riverboat nightclub, who seeks the documents for a foreign power, and Krikorian (Vittorio Massimo), pretending to be helping Mrs. Fischer but is really interested in making what he can for himself. Sofia (Dawn Addams), a cabaret star for Mrs. Fischer, is in love with von Brmmer and unwittingly endangers her life when Mrs. Fischer discovers she is helping von Brunner in his quest.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?259559</url></doc>
